    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称以色列不会针对伊朗原油，油价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/oil-drops-at-open-on-report-israel-won-t-attack-iranian-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称以色列可能不会瞄准伊朗的原油基础设施，缓解了人们对重大供应中断的担忧，油价连续第三个交易日下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/oil-drops-at-open-on-report-israel-won-t-attack-iranian-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利计划通过税率和减免向企业减免 40 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/italy-targets-4-billion-from-firms-via-tax-rates-deductions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解意大利预算计划的人士透露，意大利政府计划通过调整部分税收门槛和取消某些税收减免，向企业减免 40 亿欧元（合 44 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/italy-targets-4-billion-from-firms-via-tax-rates-deductions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 18:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京地铁首次公开募股将募资 23 亿美元，为日本六年来最大规模上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/tokyo-metro-ipo-said-to-raise-2-3-billion-in-japan-s-biggest-debut-in-six-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京地铁株式会社 (Tokyo Metro Co.) 以市场定价上限发行价发行了 3,486 亿日元（合 23 亿美元），显示出日本六年来最大规模上市交易的火爆需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/tokyo-metro-ipo-said-to-raise-2-3-billion-in-japan-s-biggest-debut-in-six-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 12:15:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
